Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sale, MEG01 – the brand new retail suite, in the prestigious Macquarie Park Village developed by Stamford Property. Macquarie Park Village is an exciting new retail and residential hub, benefiting from its landmark location moments from transport, shopping, education, employment and a wide range of health and recreation amenities.

The MPV development boasts 700 residential apartments on-site, and includes new public thoroughfares from both Epping and Herring Roads. MEG01 is located at the entrance to the MPV community off Herring Road which will benefit from both main-road exposure as well as constant foot traffic.

Some key features include;
•	Generous open floor plan of 295sqm*;
•	High exposure location with significant vehicle and foot traffic;
•	Exclusive outdoor seating area 95sqm;
•	Designed for Food & Beverage but also suitable for other uses;
•	North Eastern and South Eastern aspect with great natural lighting exposure; and
•	High ceilings with floor to ceiling glass façade on North, South and East Facades;
•      Located within the Melbourne Tower of MPV; 
•      500m to Macquarie Centre and Macquarie University Station; and
•	Visit https://mpvliving.com.au/ to find out more about Macquarie Park Village living



*Approximately, and based on information provided by the Vendor

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME RETAIL WITH EXCELLENT EXPOSURE & FIT OUT AVAILABLE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Situated at the cul de sac end of Eden Park Drive in one of Macquarie Park's best enclaves offering excellent amenity within walking distance. Approximately 150 metres from Macquarie Park Train Station and with easy access via Waterloo Road to Epping Road, Lane Cove Road and the M2 Motorway.

Rydecorp Estate is a modern office and warehouse development, consisting of 16 individual self contained units ranging from 420sqm to 1,100sqm. The estate has undergone ongoing refurbishment throughout its life to ensure tenants enjoy a quality facility that meets their staff and business needs.

Available for lease is unit 6, that provides refurbished, fitted out office with reception, perimeter offices and open plan area kitchenette all self-contained and warehouse accommodation with internal stairs down to the high clearance warehouse.

The unit consists of: 
Office: 160sqm
Warehouse: 264sqm
Total of 424sqm

The estate benefits from:
- Secure 24/7 swipe card access,
- CCTV throughout all common areas,
- 6 to 8 metre warehouse clearance, column free
- A mix of external undercover and basement car spaces
- New passenger lifts servicing all levels
- Attractive glass curtain facade providing a modern street frontage,
- The available units offer direct ground floor access to the office space, and warehouse discreetly located to the rear.
- All units are self-contained with own kitchen and amenities.

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Leasing Agents CBRE:

Peter Mangraviti 0413 750 350
